Ext.data.JsonP['Studio_4.3.0_Release_Note']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Studio 4.3.0 - 16 September 2015</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n\t\t<div id=\"banner\" class=\"confbox admonition admonition-note aui-message warning shadowed information-macro\">\n\t\t\t<p>You can now find Appcelerator documentation at <a href=\"https://docs.axway.com/\" target=\"_blank\">https://docs.axway.com/</a>. This site will be taken down in the near future.</p>\n\t\t</div>\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-46244821\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Studio 4.3.0 - 16 September 2015</h1>\n    <p>Studio 4.3.0 is a minor release that include new features and bug fixes.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46244821_Studio4.3.0ReleaseNote-NewFeatures\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>New Features</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p>Support for building, running and deploying watchOS 2 application built in Xcode    </p>\n</li><li class=\" \">    <p>Update Windows SDK Preference Page to use Windows Publisher ID    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46244821_Studio4.3.0ReleaseNote-FixedIssues\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Fixed Issues</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7385\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7385</a>: LiveView sees (dot)files as languages    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7437\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7437</a>: &quot;Sending Analytics Ping&quot; error when using a pre-4.0 workspace in 4.0 Studio    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7607\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7607</a>: Windows SDK preference page does not pick up publisher GUID from ti config    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7624\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7624</a>: Platform Configuration window does not show download and install option for Windows SDK    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7642\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7642</a>: 4.1.0.GA causing &apos;An internal error occurred during: &quot;Loading Platform Contents&quot;. java.lang.NullPointerException&apos;    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7652\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7652</a>: If you Refresh Devices, a NullPointerException is thrown    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7673\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7673</a>: Studio cannot detect Xcode 7    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7677\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7677</a>: Attempting to add new watch extension fails with error    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7683\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7683</a>: Should prompt for the name of watch app while creating Watch OS2 app in studio    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7684\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7684</a>: &apos;Create New&apos; button for Apple WatchOS 2 app is shown even though imported project already has watch app extensions    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7689\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7689</a>: Appc studio fails installation due to &quot;path too long&quot; error related to liveview    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7691\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7691</a>: Apple Watch App can be created in a project that does not have iOS deployment targets    </p>\n</li><li class=\"p1 \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/TISTUD-7706\" target=\"_blank\">TISTUD-7706</a>: Terminating a running build process will return &quot;Terminate failed&quot; dialog    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=46244821\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Studio 4.3.0 Release Note"});